title: [FSX] TechnoBrain Tokyo Haneda RJTT (RIP)
description:
[FSX] TechnoBrain Tokyo Haneda RJTT (RIP)

This was uploaded some time ago but it disappeared.

Tested RIP, no problems. Rather heavy on FPS, that's it.
Not compatible with AES, but the scenery has custom animated jetways (Crtl+J).

- Copy the included folders to the FSX Directory (Both Addon Scenery & Effects)
- Manually add 'FSAC_RJTT_FSX' to the Scenery Library

Hope you enjoy!
